Redux {
  90% use in react..
  Container where you can store your application Data
  Local Data ..
  State management Tool
  Do not belong to component state
}

uses {
  Connection btw two components
  store for fetching and adding temperory Data
}

Start :
  Architecture -> View (showing) -> Action (Collecting Data from API) 
  ->Reducer (Recieve ND store) -> Store(state of complete data in application)
  1 application - 1 Store  -> Data Unidirectional

Installation :
    npm,node,redux, react redux -> npm install redux-> npm react redux

props {
  same as react ..
}

files->redux/Container->/constants(for matching data)/services->Actions,Reducers

Add to cart {
  action send the data to store
  constant is used in Action
}


Reducer {
  Reducer takes action and Filter before sending to store
  constant is used in reducer
}

Container{
  used to connect redux and react
}

Complete Flow {
  redux wrapper in index file 
  provider
  store
}

Adding Data to cart {
  Get 1 item 
  making style for cart items
  Push multiple item in cart
  show multiple count
}

Header Component for New Component {
  to show cart item number 
}